36:31.680 --> 36:40.580
lost confidence in it. It came out in book form as Pebble in the Sky. So I
practically had to have a fist fight with him to get the manuscript away from

36:40.580 --> 36:51.080
him. And I did suggest to him too that he might consider writing non-fiction as
well as fiction since there was a much more reliable market at that time and I

36:51.080 --> 37:04.360
guess still is for non-fiction. Although by the time he actually began taking
that advice I had stopped being an agent. Okay. These questions I've been asking

37:04.360 --> 37:15.460
about as an agent as an editor and so forth just to end it could I ask you are
there any particular discoveries or influences that you're particularly proud of

37:15.460 --> 37:23.140
say things that you've had some influence in that you remember with a certain
