41:45.040 --> 41:53.720
fiction fans and I think the same has been true about the space program and
about many of the social developments of the last 20 or 30 years and I think

41:53.720 --> 42:06.080
that if you read enough science fiction you begin to get a spectrum of the
possible futures that lie ahead for all of us and I think it's quite useful in

42:06.080 --> 42:15.980
the sense that it lets you make decisions now about which ones of them you would
like to avoid or which ones you would like to avert and it helps you find ways

42:15.980 --> 42:28.620
of taking actions now that will encourage the good ones and discourage the bad
ones but it's not just that I think science fiction also has a good deal of

42:28.620 --> 42:43.580
entertainment of what is to me an extremely pleasurable kind to offer all right
you've written a great deal in your memoirs the way the future was really about

